# Tanila Robideur

Affiliation: Arcane Congress
Description: Tanila is the current head librarian of the Arcane Congress, whose library was founded by her great-great-great-great-great-great-great-great-grandfather and bears his name. Her main topic of research is pre-Galifaran thaumatology, and she is herself a talented arcanist with a focus on symbol- and glyph-related magic. She hasn't published any papers.
Location: Arcanix, Aundair
Race: Human
Role: Researcher